item.description:
In this page the customer details are input.
Customer Social title Can be selected: &ldquo;Mr.&rdquo; or &ldquo;Mrs.&rdquo;
First name This field is mandatory, when trying to save with the field empty, will show a message: &ldquo;please fill out this field.&rdquo;. Below has a help text: &ldquo;Only letters and the dot (.) character, followed by a space, are allowed.&rdquo;. When trying to save with invalid characters entered, will show an error: &ldquo;The &ldquo;First name&rdquo; field is invalid.
